projects.title: easy PAL
projects.author: Ken Pettit
projects.description: This is a simple PAL (by Matthias Musch) using shift-register based configuration

pinout.uio[0]: Config pin: This pin is used to apply the config bit that will be shifted in on a rising clock edge.
pinout.uio[1]: Enable pin: If HIGH (1) the result of the logic function is applied to all outputs.
pinout.uio[2]: Clock pin: Used for the shift register to sample in the [config pin] data (see uio[0]).
